<node CREATED="1206362044187" ID="Freemind_Link_692809682" MODIFIED="1206362051906" TEXT="appox 3 months"/>
<node CREATED="1206359536140" ID="Freemind_Link_1694475855" MODIFIED="1206359537203" TEXT="But with available high-speed computers the job can be done in about three months, and the researchers expect to have their tables completed in March. They hope to make their system available in the second quarter of this year. "/>
